  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0db6\u0dda\u0dbb\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dd0\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0dad\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dba\u0dcf \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The young man who jumped into the lake to escape from the police died",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Kurunegala police say that a young man who tried to run away after seeing a group of police officers who were guarding the Kurunegala lake area, drowned in the Kurunegala lake today (19) afternoon.",
        "The deceased youth is a 26-year-old unmarried resident of Kurunegala Thoraya Narampola area.",
        "Two youths started running away when they saw a group of police officers engaged in security while walking on the Kurunegala lake embankment section behind Kurunegala Lakdas de Mel College.",
        "Seeing this, the police officers chased the two and arrested one of the youths with great effort, but he fought with the police officers and jumped into the Kurunegala lake to escape, the police said.",
        "The young man who jumped into the lake drowned in a few moments and the police lifeguards who arrived at the scene in a few moments saved the drowned young man after an hour of searching, but he also died from drowning, the police said.",
        "Sub-Inspector Wasantha Bandara, the leader of the Kurunegala Police Life Saving Team, said that the place where the young man drowned was a very dangerous place in the lake with a depth of about 16 feet.",
        "When the young man was picked up and checked, a small quantity of drugs wrapped in a lead leaf was found in his right hand, the police said.",
        "The body of the deceased youth has been sent for a post-mortem examination at the Kurunegala Teaching Hospital on the orders of the Kurunegala Magistrate's Court.",
        "According to the instructions of Kurunegala Division Senior Superintendent of Police Mr. Upul Chandana Abeysinghe, Kurunegala Headquarters Chief Inspector of Police Mr. Kapila Adhikari is conducting further investigations."
      ],
